headline: Accenture price target lowered to $370 from $410 at Argus
summary: Argus lowered the firm’s price target on Accenture (ACN) to $370 from $410 but keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The company reported a Q3 earnings beat though the stock fell, likely on an annual decline in bookings, the analyst tells investors in a research note. headline: Trilliad Appoints Sarah Strassheim as Chief Financial Officer
summary: ANNAPOLIS, Md., June 25, 2025--Trilliad, a market-leading Growth Services Provider, is pleased to announce the appointment of Sarah Strassheim as Chief Financial Officer. A seasoned finance executive with 20+ years of experience, Sarah brings deep expertise in financial management, strategic planning, and operational excellence to her new role.
